  <shortDescription><![CDATA[<p>Whether sharing a chairlift made for two, admiring the breath-taking mountain scenery, or simply enjoying a candlelit dinner in a charming restaurant, it's easy to see that a couples ski holiday can be a truly romantic experience. But where are the most romantic ski resorts for you and your partner? We're giving you the inside knowledge to make your next Valentine's Day on the slopes the most romantic yet.</p>]]></shortDescription>
